\begin_layout Paragraph
What kind of videos are you usually watching?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The question showed that people are mostly focused on 3 kind of video :
 Music, Comedy and Documentary.
 It would be interesting to target on of those categories on the provided
 videos.
\end_layout

