\begin_layout Subsubsection
Conclusion
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To put it in a nutshell, this survey was really interesting and useful.
 Combining results of the questions asked it is possible to orient the video
 platform development and get guide lines.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
At the technical level, the choice of a desktop application is relevant
 compared to a website or a mobile application because the computer is by
 far the device used.
 Furthermore, it appear that the users are watching 2 hours per day on the
 same period of the day.
 A multicast strategy or duplication of the video content should be questioned.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
At the marketing level, the users mostly accept a delay for an expectedly
 interesting video.
 It is important to keep it in mind as on the beginning, the hosting costs
 might impede to have a big storage capacity.
 However, it is possible to compensate this by specailsing the video offer
 on one of the 3 most prefered kind of videos : Music, Comedy and Documentary.
 It could be interesting to as well to implement a ranking system in the
 application to provide interesting videos for the user.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The use of ads to finance the platform should be limited at least at the
 beginning.
 It annoy the user and could decrease the watching time or completely make
 the system unattractive at all.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Advertisement
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
history
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
From Latin, ad vertere : "to turn toward", the advertisement is a marketing
 communication to promote or sell something, usually a business's product
 or service.
 The purpose of advertisement can also to make sure that employees or shareholde
rs believe in the company.
 To be short, the advertisement is a way to convince a specific public to
 have a specific behavior 
\begin_inset Flex Emph
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
( source wiki ? https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Publicit%C3%A9#cite_note-1)
 
\end_layout

\end_inset

: buy a product, elect someone, incitement to reduce speed while driving,
 etc.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The sponsors are usually companies that are looking to improve their brand
 image or their sells.
 It could also be governments in order to make citizen aware of something
 ( like ecology or safe driving) or political personalities to raise their
 popularity.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
from television to the Internet
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If the Internet seems to become the most used media, the advertisement still
 remains present in a lot of other media.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Old media such as newspapers, magazines, Television, Radio, outdoor advertising
 or direct mail, are still widely used.
 But more and more people are using internet and the advertisement is getting
 into the new media as well as others before.
\end_layout

